    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Gordy your very own Feral Human companion. The two of you have become best friends as you wander the woods creating memories of friendship and love amongst the beauty of nature. I really hope nothing bad happens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271310/extras/64030786a9976b7c1531f242f5e47cfb.avif?t=1752253237\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271310/extras_big/64030786a9976b7c1531f242f5e47cfb.avif?t=1752253237 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gordy is a First-Person Horror Comedy that follows a hermit in the woods who befriends a feral human and work together. As the months go by a darker energy begins to take hold of the forest and you have to question if Gordy is so trust-worthy after all or maybe you're the real monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271310/extras/9cd7289c4598da65c3f5dd360bd0385e.avif?t=1752253237\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271310/extras_big/9cd7289c4598da65c3f5dd360bd0385e.avif?t=1752253237 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First Person Horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45 - 1 hour Play Time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Storyline </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend of Horror and Comedy</p></li></ul>",
